---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Sistemas de Inteligencia Artificial & Pipelines Técnicos" 
  description="Arquitectura de sistemas inteligentes y tuberías de datos de alta resiliencia. Descubre nuestras capacidades en modelos locales, ETL y robustez arquitectónica."
>
  <Navbar />

  <!-- Hero with digital network visual -->
  <section class="solutions-hero">
    <div class="glow-blur glow-cyan" style="top: 15%; right: 10%;"></div>
    <div class="container hero-grid grid-12">
      <div class="hero-left">
        <span class="badge">Sistemas AI Especializados</span>
        <h1>Soluciones AI & Arquitecturas de Datos</h1>
        <p class="large">
          Desplegamos infraestructura inteligente a la medida. Desde agentes autónomos locales hasta flujos de extracción masiva tolerantes a bloqueos.
        </p>
        <a href="#capabilities" class="btn-primary">Ver Capacidades</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-right">
        <!-- Animated Neural Network Visual -->
        <div class="neural-network-svg">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" width="100%" height="100%" class="neural-svg">
            <!-- Connection lines -->
            <line x1="100" y1="100" x2="200" y2="70" stroke="rgba(0, 157, 255, 0.4)" stroke-width="1.5" class="net-line line-1" />
            <line x1="100" y1="100" x2="200" y2="150" stroke="rgba(0, 157, 255, 0.4)" stroke-width="1.5" class="net-line line-2" />
            <line x1="100" y1="250" x2="200" y2="150" stroke="rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.4)" stroke-width="1.5" class="net-line line-3" />
            <line x1="100" y1="250" x2="200" y2="300" stroke="rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.4)" stroke-width="1.5" class="net-line line-4" />
            
            <line x1="200" y1="70" x2="300" y2="120" stroke="rgba(0, 157, 255, 0.4)" stroke-width="2" class="net-line line-5" />
            <line x1="200" y1="150" x2="300" y2="120" stroke="rgba(0, 157, 255, 0.4)" stroke-width="2" class="net-line line-6" />
            <line x1="200" y1="150" x2="300" y2="250" stroke="rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.4)" stroke-width="2" class="net-line line-7" />
            <line x1="200" y1="300" x2="300" y2="250" stroke="rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.4)" stroke-width="2" class="net-line line-8" />
            
            <line x1="300" y1="120" x2="350" y2="185" stroke="var(--color-cyan-accent)" stroke-width="2" class="net-line line-9" />
            <line x1="300" y1="250" x2="350" y2="185" stroke="var(--color-cyan-accent)" stroke-width="2" class="net-line line-10" />

            <!-- Orbit nodes -->
            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="10" fill="var(--color-primary-navy)" stroke="var(--color-electric-blue)" stroke-width="3" class="net-node node-a" />
            <circle cx="100" cy="250" r="10" fill="var(--color-primary-navy)" stroke="var(--color-electric-blue)" stroke-width="3" class="net-node node-b" />
            
            <circle cx="200" cy="70" r="12" fill="var(--color-primary-navy)" stroke="var(--color-cyan-accent)" stroke-width="3" class="net-node node-c" />
            <circle cx="200" cy="150" r="12" fill="var(--color-primary-navy)" stroke="var(--color-electric-blue)" stroke-width="3" class="net-node node-d" />
            <circle cx="200" cy="300" r="12" fill="var(--color-primary-navy)" stroke="var(--color-cyan-accent)" stroke-width="3" class="net-node node-e" />
            
            <circle cx="300" cy="120" r="14" fill="var(--color-primary-navy)" stroke="var(--color-electric-blue)" stroke-width="3" class="net-node node-f" />
            <circle cx="300" cy="250" r="14" fill="var(--color-primary-navy)" stroke="var(--color-cyan-accent)" stroke-width="3" class="net-node node-g" />
            
            <circle cx="350" cy="185" r="18" fill="var(--color-bg-dark)" stroke="var(--color-white)" stroke-width="4" class="net-node node-h" />
            <circle cx="350" cy="185" r="6" fill="var(--color-cyan-accent)" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Capabilities Section (2x3 Grid) -->
  <section class="capabilities-section" id="capabilities">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="badge">Nuestras Capacidades</span>
        <h2>Ingeniería técnica sin límites comerciales</h2>
        <p>Diseñamos componentes desacoplados y eficientes preparados para interactuar bajo escenarios de alta exigencia.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="capabilities-grid">
        <div class="card cap-card">
          <span class="cap-number">01</span>
          <div>
            <h3>LLMs Locales & Seguros</h3>
            <p>Implementación de modelos Llama, Mistral y Phi en hardware on-premises, garantizando privacidad absoluta bajo normativas estrictas de datos sin depender de APIs de terceros.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card cap-card">
          <span class="cap-number">02</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Agentes de Extracción Estructurada</h3>
            <p>Modelos cognitivos especializados en procesar PDFs, facturas y manifiestos de aduana semiestructurados, convirtiéndolos en registros JSON limpios con esquemas validados.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card cap-card">
          <span class="cap-number">03</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Crawlers Resilientes a Captchas</h3>
            <p>Bots de extracción web con rotación inteligente de proxies residenciales, simulación de navegación humana y adaptabilidad dinámica ante modificaciones del código fuente de destino.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card cap-card">
          <span class="cap-number">04</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Pipelines de Procesamiento Concurrente</h3>
            <p>Sistemas distribuidos de cola de mensajería (RabbitMQ, Apache Kafka) que procesan millones de registros diarios con consistencia garantizada y tolerancia a interrupciones.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card cap-card">
          <span class="cap-number">05</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Integraciones API & Automatización RPA</h3>
            <p>Conexión fluida de sistemas antiguos mediante emulación lógica y bots RPA robustos cuando no existen APIs disponibles o los sistemas legados están cerrados.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card cap-card">
          <span class="cap-number">06</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Instrumentación y Alarmas Técnicas</h3>
            <p>Monitoreo profundo de salud a nivel de red, consumo de RAM y tasa de rendimiento de datos con mecanismos de alerta predictiva ante anomalías.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technical Section: 5/7 Layout -->
  <section class="technical-deep-dive">
    <div class="container grid-12 tech-grid">
      <!-- Left: Technical Text (5 cols) -->
      <div class="tech-text-block">
        <span class="badge">Arquitectura del Pipeline</span>
        <h2>Cómo estructuramos un pipeline tolerante a fallos</h2>
        <p>
          No escribimos scripts improvisados. Nuestros sistemas siguen principios rigurosos de **Clean Architecture** y patrones de diseño consolidados:
        </p>
        <ul class="tech-feature-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Desacoplamiento Total:</strong> La lógica de negocio está aislada de la base de datos, APIs de terceros y frameworks web.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Circuit Breakers:</strong> Si un servicio externo falla, el sistema se aísla automáticamente y re-intenta cuando se recupera, previniendo cuellos de botella generalizados.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Capa de Validación Rigurosa:</strong> Cada dato que ingresa es sometido a validaciones de esquema (Zod/Pydantic) antes de interactuar con el dominio principal.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Re-intentos Exponenciales:</strong> Algoritmos de retry con "jitter" para suavizar los picos de peticiones y evitar baneos de IPs.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Technical Diagram (7 cols) -->
      <div class="tech-diagram-block">
        <div class="diagram-wrapper">
          <div class="diagram-header">
            <span class="dot red"></span><span class="dot yellow"></span><span class="dot green"></span>
            <span class="diagram-title">KASI Resilient Pipeline Flow</span>
          </div>
          <div class="diagram-body">
            
            <div class="diagram-node source-node">
              <span class="node-tag">IN</span>
              <span>Fuentes de Datos No Estructuradas</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="diagram-arrow">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/></svg>
            </div>
            
            <div class="diagram-node filter-node">
              <span class="node-tag">STEP 1</span>
              <span>Proxy / Desencriptación / Extracción</span>
            </div>

            <div class="diagram-arrow">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/></svg>
            </div>

            <div class="diagram-node validation-node">
              <span class="node-tag">STEP 2</span>
              <span>Esquema & Validación (Tolerancia a fallos)</span>
            </div>

            <div class="diagram-arrow">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/></svg>
            </div>

            <div class="diagram-node ai-node">
              <span class="node-tag">STEP 3</span>
              <span>Agente AI Local (Llama Parse & Normalización)</span>
            </div>

            <div class="diagram-arrow">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/></svg>
            </div>

            <div class="diagram-node destination-node">
              <span class="node-tag">OUT</span>
              <span>Destino Limpio (Data Warehouse / CRM / ERP)</span>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Big Final CTA: Build Intelligent Systems -->
  <section class="solutions-cta-section">
    <div class="container solutions-cta-box">
      <h2>¿Preparado para construir sistemas de ingeniería real?</h2>
      <p class="large">
        Diseñamos sistemas resilientes a medida que minimizan pérdidas operativas y optimizan el procesamiento de datos corporativos.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact?ref=solutions" class="btn-primary">Construir Mis Sistemas Inteligentes</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .solutions-hero {
    padding-top: calc(var(--space-12) + 40px);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-10);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-left {
    grid-column: 1 / 7;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-right {
    grid-column: 7 / 13;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .neural-network-svg {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 360px;
    height: auto;
  }

  /* Neural connections animations */
  .net-line {
    stroke-dasharray: 8;
    animation: dashLine 30s infinite linear;
  }

  .net-node {
    transform-origin: center;
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .net-node:hover {
    transform: scale(1.2);
  }

  @keyframes dashLine {
    to {
      stroke-dashoffset: -1000;
    }
  }

  /* Capabilities Grid (2x3) */
  .capabilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .cap-card {
    min-height: 240px;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }

  .cap-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-cyan-accent);
    line-height: 1;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .cap-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .cap-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Technical Deep Dive (5/7) */
  .technical-deep-dive {
    background: rgba(2, 11, 24, 0.4);
    border-block: 1px solid rgba(230, 231, 234, 0.08);
  }

  .tech-grid {
    align-items: center;
  }

  .tech-text-block {
    grid-column: 1 / 6;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .tech-feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
  }

  .tech-feature-list li {
    font-family: var(--font-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-5);
    color: var(--color-silver);
  }

  .tech-feature-list li strong {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .tech-feature-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 10px;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-cyan-accent);
  }

  .tech-diagram-block {
    grid-column: 6 / 13;
    padding-left: var(--space-5);
  }

  /* Diagram styles */
  .diagram-wrapper {
    background: rgba(6, 27, 51, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(230, 231, 234, 0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .diagram-header {
    background: rgba(2, 11, 24, 0.8);
    padding: 12px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(230, 231, 234, 0.08);
  }

  .diagram-header .dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .diagram-header .dot.red { background-color: var(--color-error); }
  .diagram-header .dot.yellow { background-color: var(--color-warning); }
  .diagram-header .dot.green { background-color: var(--color-success); }

  .diagram-title {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-silver-dark);
    margin-left: var(--space-2);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .diagram-body {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .diagram-node {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 480px;
    background: rgba(2, 11, 24, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(230, 231, 234, 0.1);
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    font-family: var(--font-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .diagram-node:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-electric-blue);
    transform: scale(1.01);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 157, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .node-tag {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.2);
    color: var(--color-cyan-accent);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .source-node { border-left: 4px solid var(--color-silver-dark); }
  .filter-node { border-left: 4px solid var(--color-electric-blue); }
  .validation-node { border-left: 4px solid var(--color-warning); }
  .ai-node { border-left: 4px solid var(--color-cyan-accent); }
  .destination-node { border-left: 4px solid var(--color-success); }

  .diagram-arrow {
    color: rgba(230, 231, 234, 0.3);
    animation: floatArrow 2s infinite ease-in-out;
  }

  @keyframes floatArrow {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(4px); color: var(--color-electric-blue); }
  }

  /* Solutions CTA Box */
  .solutions-cta-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-8);
  }

  .solutions-cta-box {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 60%), var(--grad-dark-card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(230, 231, 234, 0.08);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .solutions-cta-box h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem);
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .solutions-cta-box p {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .hero-left {
      grid-column: span 12;
      text-align: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }

    .hero-right {
      grid-column: span 12;
    }

    .capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .tech-text-block {
      grid-column: span 12;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }

    .tech-diagram-block {
      grid-column: span 12;
      padding-left: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .solutions-hero {
      padding-top: calc(var(--space-10) + 60px);
    }

    .cap-card {
      min-height: auto;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-3);
    }

    .solutions-cta-box {
      padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-5);
    }

    .solutions-cta-box .btn-primary {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
